<h2 class="bold font-l">Nyakuza Metro</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The trains in the Nyakuza Metro level are all pulled by gigantic cats. They also serve as a stage hazard that Hat Kid must avoid. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ChariotPulledByCats" class='trope-example-link'>Chariot Pulled by Cats</a></p>
</div>
