<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Nyakuza Metro</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The trains in the Nyakuza Metro level are all pulled by gigantic cats. They also serve as a stage hazard that Hat Kid must avoid.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="zvrk97">
